---
title: Quick Hoisin Pork Meatballs & Jasmine Rice with Sesame Greens & Peanuts
description: This meal is really quick – your greens will be ready in a flash and little hands can help form meatballs in record time. Really, for
such a speedy effort you'll be delighted with how good this dinner tastes.
